snippet.title: The Definitive Classic Sonic Experience (Sonic Generations)
snippet.description:
(No Commentary Showcase) In this video, I show off Classic Sonic Improvement Mod 7.0 for Sonic Generations. This MASSIVE update completely overhauls Classic Sonic in a multitude of different ways, including a brand new Classic design, Super Peel out and Drop Dash abilities, tweaked physics, and much more.
#Sonic #SonicGenerations #SonicTheHedgehog

🔔 CLICK THE BELL AND TURN ON ALL NOTIFICATIONS

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gH7YuuV8BuQ

https://gamebanana.com/gamefiles/10739
